  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588240/extras/7705bf70365851ce1b34bd4af581b22e.avif?t=1773935126\" width=600 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588240/extras/99759f1b6a53d18363a49bcce534dbaf.avif?t=1773935126\" width=600 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588240/extras/9bb1b20b5e04292df3b0da5bfe164ca4.avif?t=1773935126\" width=600 height=120 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-ROCKET JUMP</strong> across platforms and up walls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-GRAPPLE HOOK</strong> the terrain to swing through danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -<strong>GROUND POUND</strong> to transform into a thunderbolt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -<strong>SPEEDRUN</strong> every level at lightning-speed! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no max velocity and instant respawns, nothing is holding you back from blazing an electric trail through every level. As the challenges get harder, you'll only get faster.</p>",
